Now, I love how some people want to force their religion down others throats. The sanctimonious arrogance! Your belief in the non-existence of a god is your right, but your non-god is better than my god? If someone has a superstition that makes them live a more moral life, good. If they believe the blue fairy will fly out of their arse and spank them should they do wrong, so be it. <br>
